videos.description: UConn head coach Geno Auriemma wears a Kobe Bryant jersey before the Huskies take on the Oregon Ducks.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Auriemma wears Kobe jersey during matchup with Oregon) 2020/02/03

videos.headline: Auriemma wears Kobe jersey during matchup with Oregon

videos.description: Oregon's Satou Sabally knocks down a 3-pointer right at the first-quarter buzzer.
videos.headline: Sabally's 3 beats the first-quarter buzzer

videos.description: Olivia Nelson-Ododa gets the pass then throws it right back to Aubre Griffin for the easy layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (UConn runs give-and-go to perfection for the Griffin layup) 2020/02/03

videos.headline: UConn runs give-and-go to perfection for the Griffin layup

videos.description: Sabrina Ionescu throws the perfect back-door pass to Erin Boley for the easy layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Ionescu drops a dime to Boley for the layup) 2020/02/03

videos.headline: Ionescu drops a dime to Boley for the layup

videos.description: Sabrina Ionescu comes off the screen and drains the 3-pointer extending the Ducks' lead.

videos.headline: Ionescu bottoms a 3 from the top of the key

videos.description: Crystal Dangerfield gets out in transition and gets the tough and-1 layup to fall plus the foul.

videos.headline: Dangerfield gets the tough layup to go

videos.description: Sabrina Ionescu, Ruthy Hebard and Satou Sabally all have big games to help Oregon take down UConn 74-56 on the road.
